<item chapterid="606268" siteid="0" sourceid="0" sourcecid="0" sourcecorder="0" articleid="1943" articlename="假面娇妻" volumeid="0" posterid="1" poster="admin" postdate="1521806441" lastupdate="1521806441" chaptername="第一百四十四章替我向魏辉问好" chapterorder="144" size="6102" saleprice="0" salenum="0" totalcost="0" attachment="" summary="    宁纪的脸黑了，建叔你干嘛？好像只有在躲子弹的时候，才走S形吧。

